quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  2,62,"jo log musalman hain ya yahodi ya isaai ya sitara parast, ( yani koi shakhs kisi qoum o mazhab ka ho ) jo khuda aur roz qayamat par imaan laaye ga, aur naik amal kere ga, to aisay logon ko un ( ke aamaal ) ka sila khuda ke haan miley ga aur ( qayamat ke din ) un ko nah kisi terhan ka khauf hoga aur nah woh gham naak hon ge"
  2,63,"aur jab hum ne tum se ehad ( kar ) liya aur koh-e tor ko tum par utha kharakiya ( aur hukum diya ) ke jo kitaab hum ne tum ko di hai, is ko zor se pakdae raho, aur jo is mein ( likha ) hai, usay yaad rakho, taakay ( azaab se ) mehfooz raho"
  2,64,to tum is ke baad ( ehad se ) phir gay aur agar tum par khuda ka fazl aur is ki meharbani nah hoti to tum khasaray mein parre gay hotay
  2,65,"aur tum un logon ko khoob jantay hon, jo tum mein se haftay ke din ( machhli ka shikaar karne ) mein hadd se tajawaz kar gay they, to hum ne un se kaha ke zaleel vkhwar bandar ho jao"
  2,66,aur is qissay ko is waqt ke logon ke liye aur jo un ke baad anay walay they Ibrat aur parhaiz gaaron ke liye nasiyaat bana diya
  2,67,"aur jab moose ne apni qoum ke logon se kaha ke khuda tum ko hukum deta hai ke aik bail zibah karo. woh bolay,kiya tum hum se hansi karte ho. ( moose ne ) kaha ke mein allah ki panah mangta hon ke nadaan banon"
  2,68,"unhon ne kaha ke apne perwar-digaar se iltija kijiyej ke woh hamein yeh betaye ke woh bail kis terhan ka ho. ( moose ne ) kaha ke perwar-digaar farmata hai ke woh bail nah to boorha ho aur nah bitchrha, balkay un ke darmain ( yani jawan ) ho. jaissa tum ko hukum diya gaya hai, waisa karo"
  2,69,"unhon ne kaha ke perwar-digaar se darkhwast kijiyej ke hum ko yeh bhi betaye ke is ka rang kaisa ho. moose ne kaha, perwar-digaar farmata hai ke is ka rang gehra zard ho ke dekhnay walon ( ke dil ) ko khush kar deta ho"
